Body Worn Cameras
Most Versatile Body Camera on the Market
Digital Ally™ designs and manufactures the most versatile body camera on the market. Choose from a one-piece or two-piece design. Each unit comes with a variety of mounts and camera modules that help meet your agency's needs.






FirstVu HD | FirstVu HD One
View Flyer





Protection for everyone!
Officers and general public covered
Studies have consistently shown that by deploying body worn cameras, agencies see a reduction in the number of complaints and use of force incidents. With permanent metadata embedded in every video, agencies can be confident that their evidence will be the highest quality and maintain strict chain of custody and audit requirements for prosecution.






With the ability to automatically activate our FirstVu HD body-worn cameras and in-car video systems with the company's patented VuLink® technology, our officers no longer have to think about pressing a button to record interactions. This functionality allows to meet our goals of increasing the safety for our officers while ensuring that we capture a comprehensive perspective of the event.
-Sheriff Rick Clark | Pickens County Sheriff's Office






The Right Tool For The Job
One size does NOT fit all!






Compare our Models










Two-Piece Solution
FirstVu HD 
The FirstVu HD two-piece model can be mounted on an officer's chest, pouch, shoulder, helmet, belt, or vehicle. 






One-Piece Solution
FirstVu HD One
The FirstVu HD one-piece model gives agencies an additional option when choosing which body worn camera to purchase. The FirstVu HD One builds upon the same platform as our two piece model.









High Definition Video & Audio
720p Resolution with 130 degree angle field of view
The camera captures exactly what the officer sees during the incident. HD Audio recording built into the camera.












Videos On The Go
Digital Ally's VuVault® platform continues to expand with the VuVault® mobile application for Android and iOS.








VuVault®
In the Palm of Every Officer
The app allows for full system control including the ability to view the video feed, add notes and play back recorded videos. You also have the ability to view the remaining storage space and battery life. VuVaultGO® allows for secure access to recordings and camera controls, GPS & event tagging. VuVaultGO® is included with every FirstVu HD purchase.






Docking Stations
Station Headquarters | Office/Home-Use
Our two Dock options allow your agency to upload your FirstVu HD Body Worn Camera video evidence the way you want to. Choose from either our 12-unit Smart Docking Station or our One-Unit portable Dock you can place in your desk or store at home. Both docking stations can automatically upload recorded videos on to your VuVault® server or onto your VuVault.Com® cloud service.















Industry's only "Smart Dock"
Secure Timely Transfer | "Plug & Play"
Our 12-Unit Smart Docking Station has a 500GB Local Memory hard drive that allows for a faster transfer of data to local or cloud software storage. This unit also can simultaneously upload 4 hours per 12 FirstVu HD cameras within a 15 minute shift change. All of this while charging units and making updates to any configuration needed for your devices.









